A WEB application for automating the accounting of student progress 
with authorization and access rights based on roles (student, teacher, admin), 
developed using the MVC design pattern and the following technologies:

- Java EE, Apache Maven
- WAR. Tomcat web container. Servlets
- Server-side technologies: HTTP
- Client-side technologies: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (base), Bootstrap 
- Database to store and retrieve information from (MySQL, queries, DB configuration in IntelliJ IDEA)
- Cookies setting and configuring

 Development environment: IntelliJ IDEA
 
